641
00:30:27,405 --> 00:30:32,495
hot im dos gefeln. a yid arbet baym, bay, bay der erd, dos hot er nokh nisht gezen.

642
00:30:32,569 --> 00:30:34,773
er hot zikh direkt farlibt in mayn ABA

643
00:30:34,864 --> 00:30:37,085
un dos hot undz geratevet dos lebn.

644
00:30:37,412 --> 00:30:38,464
far vos?

645
00:30:38,464 --> 00:30:42,131
vayl di pre- froy fun dem preferkt iz geven a groyse klavte.

646
00:30:42,238 --> 00:30:44,614
m'hot zi gerufn di klavte fun Mogilev

647
00:30:44,614 --> 00:30:49,154
iz zi gekumen eyn mol in gortn azoy vi zi, der, der prefekt iz dort, der, der porets.

648
00:30:49,154 --> 00:30:52,309
hot zi gezogt "di un di blumen vil ikh bay mir in gortn hobn."

649
00:30:52,309 --> 00:30:54,064
un dos iz geven herbst.

650
00:30:54,064 --> 00:30:58,112
shoyn farn vinter. hot mayn pape, hot gekent nor daytshn redn

651
00:30:58,455 --> 00:30:59,793
nisht rumenish

652
00:30:59,793 --> 00:31:00,711
hot er gezogt

653
00:31:00,801 --> 00:31:01,971
"SCHADE"

654
00:31:01,971 --> 00:31:03,633
SCHADE heyst a shod

655
00:31:03,633 --> 00:31:05,493
"di blumen veln nisht vaksn."

656
00:31:05,493 --> 00:31:09,573
zi hot farshtanen dos vort SCHADE az far ir iz dos a shod tsu gebn

657
00:31:09,573 --> 00:31:13,434
iz zi gegangen aheym un hot gemakht farn man a nervn KRISE

658
00:31:13,609 --> 00:31:18,783
hot der man genumen a tsetele un geshribn "familye Marmorosh in fir un tsvontsik sho

659
00:31:18,891 --> 00:31:20,218
ibern Bug."

660
00:31:20,292 --> 00:31:22,232
dos iz geven Dnyester, Bug.

661
00:31:22,232 --> 00:31:26,362
un baym, ibern Bug hobn di daytshn, ver s'iz gekumen fun yidn iber tsu zey

662
00:31:26,362 --> 00:31:27,682
hobn zey SOFORT geharget.

663
00:31:27,781 --> 00:31:29,145
dos iz geven der sof.

664
00:31:29,218 --> 00:31:31,004
un ikh bin gelofn tsu dem

